name: WannaBe - Prototype
description:
WannaBe is a life simulator where you live each stage of someone's life. You make choices, form relationships, and gain skills that get carried over as you age.  The prototype consists of the baby life stage. 

--

What you see here is a prototype of the game. The point of uploading it is to get feedback and ideas on where to take the product. Let us know what was confusing about the game or what you would like to add.
